name: TimesTableTutor
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: times table tutor
des: Alexa will practice your multiplication tables with you! Give Alexa which multiplication table you want to practice, and then Alexa will randomly generate questions for you to answer! The table you want to practice is up to you! The number of questions that you want to be asked is up to you! Practice with Alexa!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
